long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
orwell.gg is a primary source of truth for all passionate gamers that are looking for a place where they can browse all current, upcoming or past competitive matches; get their result or watch VODs. In addition to matches, we bring you current news from gaming world, game update notes, community reddit posts and even a place where you can browse all currently LIVE streams.
Install our extension and never miss any news from gaming world.

For improvment suggestions, bugs or any questionst contact us at extension@orwell.gg
